name.ja: パラレル・テレポート

text.en: Tribute 1 Psychic monster that has a Level; Special Summon 1 Level 7 or lower Psychic monster from your Deck or Extra Deck, then, if those monsters' original Levels are different, you lose LP equal to the difference x 1000. You cannot Special Summon the turn you activate this card, except Psychic monsters. You can only activate 1 "Parallel Teleport" per turn.
